==[[Virginia Tech massacre|Shooting Controversies]]==
JuicyCampus is a popular place to talk about shooting up your school. In December of 2007, Loyola Maymount senior Carlos Huerta decided to post on JuicyCampus  and [[b/|/b/]] predicting an upcoming massacre at his college. He was promply [[Partyvan]]ned.

